s?</p><p>I'm not entirely sure how they could be applied to ALS patients, but it certainly would offer a chance of not just living longer, but maybe some day gaining back some function.</p><p>By choosing death, you will be forfeiting any chance of being helped by these potential new technologies.  By choosing ... <span class="read-more-button">(read more)</span></p></div></div></div><div class="CommentBottom-bottom"><div class="CommentBottom-leftSection"><a class="comments-item-reply-link CommentsItem-replyLink">Reply</a></div><div class="CommentBottom-rightSection"><span class="NamesAttachedReactionsVoteOnComment-footerReactionsRow"><span class=""><span class="NamesAttachedReactionsVoteOnComment-addReactionButton react-hover-style"><svg height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><g fill="currentColor"><path d="m13 7c0-3.31371-2.6863-6-6-6-3.31371 0-6 2.68629-6 6 0 3.3137 2.68629 6 6 6 .08516 0 .1699-.0018.25419-.0053-.11154-.3168-.18862-.6499-.22673-.9948l-.02746.0001c-2.76142 0-5-2.23858-5-5s2.23858-5 5-5 5 2.23858 5 5l-.0001.02746c.3449.03811.678.11519.9948.22673.0035-.08429.0053-.16903.0053-.25419z"></path><path d="m7.11191 10.4982c.08367-.368.21246-.71893.38025-1.04657-.15911.03174-.32368.04837-.49216.04837-.74037 0-1.40506-.3212-1.86354-.83346-.18417-.20576-.50026-.22327-.70603-.03911-.20576.18417-.22327.50026-.03911.70603.64016.71524 1.57205 1.16654 2.60868 1.16654.03744 0 .07475-.0006.11191-.0018z"></path><path d="m6 6c0 .41421-.33579.75-.75.75s-.75-.33579-.75-.75.33579-.75.75-.75.75.33579.75.75z"></path><path d="m8.75 6.75c.41421 0 .75-.33579.75-.75s-.33579-.75-.75-.75-.75.33579-.75.75.33579.75.75.75z"></path><path d="m15 11.5c0 1.933-1.567 3.5-3.5 3.5s-3.5-1.567-3.5-3.5 1.567-3.5 3.5-3.5 3.5 1.567 3.5 3.5zm-3-2c0-.27614-.2239-.5-.5-.5s-.5.22386-.5.5v1.5h-1.5c-.27614 0-.5.2239-.5.5s.22386.5.5.5h1.5v1.5c0 .2761.2239.5.5.5s.5-.2239.5-.5v-1.5h1.5c.2761 0 .5-.2239.5-.5s-.2239-.5-.5-.5h-1.5z"></path></g></svg></span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></